title: The Magnetic Fields Discography
description:
The magnetic fields discography. An amazing collection of pretty much all their music including a solo album from Stephen Merritt himself. 

    
Distant Plastic Trees (1991)
    
The Wayward Bus (1992)
    
The House of Tomorrow (EP) (1992)
    
The Charm of the Highway Strip (1994)
    
Holiday (1994)
    
Get Lost (1995)
    
69 Love Songs (1999)
    
i (2004)
    
Distortion (2008)
    
Realism (2010)
    
Love at the Bottom of the Sea (2012)

BONUS ALBUM!!

Pieces of April (2003)

Enjoy and SEEEEEEEEEEED!
